697
00:51:04,119 --> 00:51:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] Onda i s tim treba izaći u javnost.

698
00:51:05,579 --> 00:51:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] Zvali smo policiju,

699
00:51:06,440 --> 00:51:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] nije htjela doći.

700
00:51:07,659 --> 00:51:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] Ali policiji treba pomoć.

701
00:51:09,239 --> 00:51:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo ste u pravu.

702
00:51:10,519 --> 00:51:11,599
[SPEAKER_01] Treba im dojavljivati.

703
00:51:11,599 --> 00:51:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Gledajte, tu smo uočili,

704
00:51:13,139 --> 00:51:13,900
[SPEAKER_01] ovdje smo uočili.

705
00:51:13,900 --> 00:51:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ako vi kažete

706
00:51:14,840 --> 00:51:16,059
[SPEAKER_01] 10 poziva,

707
00:51:16,059 --> 00:51:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] naočili smo na tom i tom dijelu

708
00:51:18,300 --> 00:51:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] da prolaze migranti.

709
00:51:20,079 --> 00:51:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] E upravo je to ono

710
00:51:21,480 --> 00:51:22,420
[SPEAKER_01] o čemu ja pričam.

711
00:51:22,420 --> 00:51:24,320
[SPEAKER_01] Onda ćemo tu napraviti blokadu,

712
00:51:24,320 --> 00:51:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] tu ćemo napraviti punkt,

713
00:51:25,500 --> 00:51:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] tu ćemo i čekati.

714
00:51:26,460 --> 00:51:27,780
[SPEAKER_01] Policija isto ne može

715
00:51:27,780 --> 00:51:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] to cijelo područje znati

716
00:51:29,420 --> 00:51:30,340
[SPEAKER_01] gdje oni prolaze.

717
00:51:30,340 --> 00:51:31,659
[SPEAKER_01] Oni isto mijenjaju rute.

718
00:51:31,659 --> 00:51:32,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam da su...

719
00:51:32,480 --> 00:51:33,940
[SPEAKER_00] I kako to možemo promijeniti?

720
00:51:33,940 --> 00:51:35,519
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, kako može biti

721
00:51:35,519 --> 00:51:37,159
[SPEAKER_00] s jedne strane od strane građana

722
00:51:37,159 --> 00:51:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] više povjerenja

723
00:51:38,000 --> 00:51:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] u policijski sustav,

724
00:51:39,119 --> 00:51:39,780
[SPEAKER_00] a s druge strane...

725
00:51:39,780 --> 00:51:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, svima nam je to u cilju.

726
00:51:41,599 --> 00:51:42,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što nije?

727
00:51:42,059 --> 00:51:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] Da budemo malo sigurniji.

728
00:51:43,460 --> 00:51:46,119
[SPEAKER_01] Bojim se da mi jesmo

729
00:51:46,119 --> 00:51:47,659
[SPEAKER_01] EU, ali da još uvijek

730
00:51:47,659 --> 00:51:49,380
[SPEAKER_01] imamo taj balkanski mentalitet

731
00:51:49,380 --> 00:51:50,679
[SPEAKER_01] u glavi da je tu problem.

732
00:51:50,679 --> 00:51:51,800
[SPEAKER_00] Znači nemoj se zamjerati.

733
00:51:51,800 --> 00:51:53,639
[SPEAKER_01] Da je tu taj problem ovoga, da.

734
00:51:53,639 --> 00:51:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ja ću vam reći

735
00:51:56,639 --> 00:51:58,119
[SPEAKER_01] ovoga...

736
00:51:58,119 --> 00:51:59,119
[SPEAKER_01] Vozio sam se...

737
00:51:59,119 --> 00:52:00,239
[SPEAKER_01] Vozio sam se...

738
00:52:00,239 --> 00:52:00,900
[SPEAKER_01] Moram to reći.

739
00:52:00,900 --> 00:52:02,239
[SPEAKER_01] Vozio sam se u autu

740
00:52:02,239 --> 00:52:04,579
[SPEAKER_01] i vidio sam osoba ispred mene

741
00:52:04,579 --> 00:52:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] je u Zagrebu na mostu

742
00:52:06,099 --> 00:52:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] otvorila prozor

743
00:52:07,239 --> 00:52:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] i bacila je torbu u Savu.

744
00:52:10,019 --> 00:52:11,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam zapamtio

745
00:52:11,960 --> 00:52:13,119
[SPEAKER_01] registarsku oznaku.

746
00:52:13,119 --> 00:52:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nazvo sam ovoga OKC

747
00:52:15,440 --> 00:52:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] i rekao sam ovoga

748
00:52:17,340 --> 00:52:18,820
[SPEAKER_01] gledajte, iz tog i tog vozila

749
00:52:18,820 --> 00:52:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] je izbačena torba,

750
00:52:20,619 --> 00:52:21,760
[SPEAKER_01] vozila je to i to.

751
00:52:21,760 --> 00:52:25,260
[SPEAKER_01] A joj, što ću sada...

752
00:52:25,260 --> 00:52:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] Mi bi trebali zvati onda

753
