754
00:52:27,159 --> 00:52:28,019
[SPEAKER_01] Jel im?

755
00:52:28,019 --> 00:52:28,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ne morate vi zvati

756
00:52:28,760 --> 00:52:29,619
[SPEAKER_01] policijske ronijace.

757
